# Bayram, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Bayram () is a rural locality (a selo) in Karlanyurtovsky Selsoviet, Khasavyurtovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia.  There are 14 streets.
Geography
Bayram is located 8&nbsp;km east of Khasavyurt (the district's administrative centre) by road. Petrakovskoye is the nearest rural locality.
